{
  "name": "Rest Hold",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/wrestling.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a move action while you are grappling an adjacent creature, you may regain your martial focus and treat that creature as granting you partial cover until the start of your next turn. If an attack misses your AC by 2 or less, compare the result to the grappled creature&#8217;s AC; if the attack roll would hit the grappled creature&#8217;s AC, resolve the attack as though the grappled creature was the original target. You cannot use this ability if you do not control the grapple.</p>\n",
